    "In Table I, we detail various reasoning failures, each illustrated with an example.",
    "Structural Limitations: These issues occur when knowledge becomes inaccessible due to limitations in the structural design of the knowledge base or inefficient processing methods.",
    "In Table I, we categorize these challenges under structural issues, limited query processing, and the selection of inappropriate evaluation metrics.In this work, our primary focus is on addressing errors stemming from reasoning failures in LLM models and enhancing their reasoning capabilities.",
